==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Opportunism
<hw>Op`por*tun"ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>opportunisme</ets>.]</ety> <def>The art or practice of taking
advantage of opportunities or circumstances, or of seeking immediate
advantage with little regard for ultimate consequences.</def>
<mark>[Recent]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Opportunist</ent>⟦br⟧
